        "TileImage": "$($repository daa6a057-d25c-488e-96e4-1a36aed4b994).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon 47!\r\rYour next target of location is a vineyard in Mendoza, Argentina. Our client, a reputable vineyard has learned that their competitor Yates Vines has came up with a secret recipe that would surely beat everyone else out of the market of luxurious wines. They hired us to take out the three employees who know the recipe, the chief vinemaker, the sommelier, and a very talented worker who is just about to be promoted for his contribution.\r\rGood luck 47!",
